---
// About Text Section Component
---

<section class="about-text-section">
  <div class="section-content">
    <div class="text-content">
      <h2 class="section-title">About Our Platform</h2>
      <p class="section-text">
        Our cutting-edge platform revolutionizes the way you interact with modern web applications. 
        Built with performance and user experience at its core, we deliver seamless functionality 
        across all devices and screen sizes.
      </p>
      <p class="section-text">
        From lightning-fast load times to intuitive user interfaces, every aspect of our platform 
        is designed to exceed expectations. We combine the latest web technologies with thoughtful 
        design principles to create experiences that truly matter.
      </p>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Performance First</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Optimized for speed with minimal load times</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Mobile Responsive</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Perfect experience on any device size</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Modern Design</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Clean, contemporary interfaces that users love</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Reliable Support</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">24/7 customer support when you need it</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-text-section {
    height: 900px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .section-content {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--container-padding);
  }

  .text-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: var(--line-height-tight);
  }

  .section-text {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .feature-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .feature-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .feature-description {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--line-height-normal);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    }

    .section-text {
      font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    }
  }
</style>